&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Anthropic&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anthropic’s mission is to create reliable, interpretable, and steerable AI systems. We want AI to be safe and beneficial for our users and for society as a whole. Our team is a quickly growing group of committed researchers, engineers, policy experts, and business leaders working together to build beneficial AI systems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an Internal Mobility Specialist to join Anthropic&#39;s People team. In this role, you will build our internal mobility program from the ground up and maintain it over time, creating pathways that help employees grow their careers while meeting the evolving needs of our rapidly scaling organization. You&#39;ll be the go-to expert for all things related to internal transfers, working at the intersection of People Operations, Recruiting, Finance, and Legal to create seamless experiences for employees exploring new opportunities within Anthropic.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a highly cross-functional role where you&#39;ll develop strategy while also rolling up your sleeves to handle day-to-day operations. If you thrive in building new programs, enjoy solving complex operational challenges, and care deeply about employee development, this role might be a great fit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement a comprehensive internal mobility program strategy aligned with Anthropic&#39;s objectives and business needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage day-to-day operations for internal transfers, including mobility logistics and data processing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a trusted resource and guide for employees interested in pursuing new internal opportunities and managers interested in internal talent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify trends in mobility patterns and proactively address process and policy gaps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate effective communication and collaboration across stakeholders including employees, managers, People Partners, People Analytics, Recruiting, Immigration, Global Mobility, Finance, Tax, Compensation, and Payroll&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop user-friendly documentation, enablement materials, and training resources to educate partner teams on internal mobility programs and processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and track key metrics to measure the success and impact of internal mobility initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
